result:
.label-wrapper
    .list
        display flex
        flex-wrap wrap
        .label-item
            margin 10px 8px 10px 0
            padding: 3px 8px;
            background #EEEEEE
            color #333333
            border-radius 2px
            cursor pointer
            font-size 12px
            &.on
                color #fff
                background #1890FF
    .footer
        display flex
        justify-content flex-end
        margin-top 40px
        button
            margin-left 10px
.btn
    width 60px
    height 24px
.title
    font-size 13px
.list-box
		overflow-y auto
		overflow-x hidden
		max-height 240px
